Code book

I Information about source files to creat the required data set
After analysing which variables are required, the following files are needed for this project.

1. Subject
The observations for all subjects for both training and test come from the file: 
file_subject_train = "./UCI HAR Dataset/train/subject_train.txt"
file_subject_test = "./UCI HAR Dataset/test/subject_test.txt"

2. Activity 
The ativity expressioin and labels come from the file:
file_activity_labels="./UCI HAR Dataset/activity_labels.txt"

The observations of all activities for all measurements for both training and test come from:
file_activity_label_train = "./UCI HAR Dataset/train/y_train.txt"
file_activity_label_test = "./UCI HAR Dataset/test/y_test.txt"

3. Only on the mean and standard deviation for each measurement. 
The information was extracted from V2 of the file:
file_features = "./UCI HAR Dataset/features.txt". 
Those measurment names, units are kept as same as explination in the source files 

The observations for all measurements for both training and test came from 
file_data_train = "./UCI HAR Dataset/train/X_train.txt"
file_data_test  = "./UCI HAR Dataset/test/X_test.txt"

