III The tidy data
The first order of the didy data set is that the subject column is sorted by default ascending order from 1 to 30. 
The seconder order is that for each subject the activity column is sorted by default ascending order based on the 
activity labels from 1 to 6, not based on the letters of activity name words. Each observation data in the tidy data 
set from column 3 to 68 is the averages for each meansurement.

IV write the data set to txt file. 
To simplify, all characters are shown without quote.
